<!-- Main -->
<section class="wrapper style1">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row gtr-200">

      <%= render "articles/sidebar_left" %>

      <div class="col-6 col-12-narrower imp-narrower">
        <div id="content">

          <!-- Content -->

          <article>
            <header>
              <h2>Resources on Well-being and Mental Health</h2>
            </header>

            <h3>English-language:</h3>

            <h6>Greater Good Science Center (UC Berkeley)</h6>
            <p>https://greatergood.berkeley.edu</p>
            <p>A website dedicated to research on well-being, empathy, and positive psychology – featuring numerous articles, videos, and tools to help understand how to develop healthy emotional habits.</p>

            <h6>Mindful</h6>
            <p>https://www.mindful.org</p>
            <p>Resources on mindfulness, meditation, and stress management techniques. Many guides and articles that facilitate integrating mindfulness practices into daily life.</p>

            <h6>Psychology Today – Mindfulness & Wellbeing</h6>
            <p>https://www.psychologytoday.com/us/basics/mindfulness</p>
            <p>Articles by psychology experts discussing mindfulness techniques, coping with stress, and building well-being.</p>

            <h6>Verywell Mind</h6>
            <p>https://www.verywellmind.com</p>
            <p>A wide selection of content on mental health, relaxation techniques, and self-help, written in simple language.</p>

            <h6>PositivePsychology</h6>
            <p>https://positivepsychology.com</p>
            <p>Practical tools, articles, and research on positive psychology that can help build better well-being.</p>

            <br>
            <h3>Polish-language:</h3>

            <h6>Psychologia w Praktyce</h6>
            <p>https://psychologiawpraktyce.pl</p>
            <p>A portal offering articles and interviews with specialists on psychological topics, including well-being and stress management.</p>

            <h6>Zdrowie Psychiczne – Poradnik Zdrowie</h6>
            <p>https://zdrowie.gazeta.pl/psychologia</p>
            <p>A section dedicated to mental health, offering practical advice, case studies, and reviews of methods for managing one’s emotions.</p>

            <h6>PositivePsychology</h6>
            <p>https://positivepsychology.com</p>
            <p>Practical tools, articles, and research on positive psychology that can help build better well-being.</p>

            <br>
            <h3>Books – Recommended Reading</h3>
            <h3>English-language:</h3>

            <h6>“The Power of Now” – Eckhart Tolle</h6>
            <p>A classic about presence and living in the moment. This book teaches how to reduce stress and improve quality of life through conscious breathing and mindfulness.</p>

            <h6>“Emotional Intelligence: Why It Can Matter More Than IQ” – Daniel Goleman</h6>
            <p>A groundbreaking book showing how emotional intelligence affects life and career success, and how its development can improve well-being.</p>

            <h6>“The How of Happiness” – Sonja Lyubomirsky</h6>
            <p>A practical guide based on research, providing strategies to increase happiness and well-being by changing habits.</p>

            <h6>“Emotional Agility: Get Unstuck, Embrace Change, and Thrive in Work and Life” – Susan David</h6>
            <p>A book about emotional agility, helping to cope with difficulties, accept change, and develop positive habits.</p>

            <h6>“The Happiness Advantage” – Shawn Achor</h6>
            <p>The author demonstrates how a positive mindset leads to better life and work outcomes, presenting scientific methods to increase happiness.</p>

            <br>
            <h3>Polish-language:</h3>

            <h6>“Uważność. Trening uważności dla początkujących” – Mark Williams, Danny Penman (Polish version)</h6>
            <p>A practical guide to mindfulness and meditation, offering exercises to reduce stress and improve well-being.</p>

            <h6>“Cisza. Siła introwersji w świecie, który nie może przestać mówić” – Susan Cain (Polish translation)</h6>
            <p>An inspiring book showing the value of silence and reflection in everyday life, ideal for those seeking balance.</p>

            <h6>“Inteligencja emocjonalna” – Daniel Goleman (Polish version)</h6>
            <p>A classic explaining how emotions shape our lives and why emotional intelligence is key to mental health.</p>

          </article>

        </div>
      </div>

      <%= render "articles/sidebar_right" %>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
